lead_paragraph: A teen who fatally shot another student at his suburban Denver high school last year had been deemed "not a high-level of threat" after shouting a death threat against his debate coach three months earlier, according to documents obtained by The Associated Press.

headline.main: APNewsBreak: Teen Gunman Deemed Not a High Threat
